<h2>Sensors</h2>
<p>Sensors available in the library:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>name</th>
<th>Unit</th>
<th align="left">Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>current_power</td>
<td>W</td>
<td align="left">Current power generated by the inverter.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>today_yield</td>
<td>kWh</td>
<td align="left">Power yield for today.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>today_time</td>
<td>h</td>
<td align="left">Inverterâ€™s running time for today.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>today_max_current</td>
<td>W</td>
<td align="left">Maximum current power for today. (only for connection via ethernet module)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>total_yield</td>
<td>kWh</td>
<td align="left">Total kWh generated to date.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>total_time</td>
<td>h</td>
<td align="left">Total running time of the inverter.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>total_co2_reduced</td>
<td>kg</td>
<td align="left">Total CO2 in kg reduced.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>temperature</td>
<td>Â°C</td>
<td align="left">Temperature of the inverter.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>state</td>
<td>N/A</td>
<td align="left">Live state of the inverter.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2>Full configuration example for WiFi inverters</h2>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">sensor:
  - platform: saj
    name: MY_INVERTER_NAME
    host: IP_ADDRESS_OF_DEVICE
    type: wifi
    username: USERNAME
    password: PASSWORD
</code></pre>
